name: Shirley Weber, PhD
tweet: @AlexPadilla4CA has led the Secretary of State with distinction and purpose, and California is better for it. I look forward to continuing his work while doubling down on his dedication to protecting the right to vote, as well as inspiring greater trust in our election systems.

name: Shirley Weber, PhD
tweet: I am excited to be nominated for this historical appointment as the Secretary of State of California. I thank ⁦@CAgovernor⁩ for the confidence in me. Being the first Black Woman in this position will be monumental and I am up for the challenge.  https://t.co/NMTZgX5HfC
